                     <interp inst="t18200918-265-off1517" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200918-265-cd1518" type="crimeDate">31st of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-265-off1517 t18200918-265-cd1518"></join>, one watch, value 3 l.; one chain, value 1 l.; two seals, value 1 l., and two keys, value 3 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-265-victim2477" type="victimName">
                           John 
